text:
Celebrations, Parades and Municipal Events: A two minute devotional period in memoriam to the World War dead. Times Square, south from West 44th Street, showing Broadway on the left and Seventh Ave. on the right; dividing same is the apex formed by the Times Building.
November 11, 1929.

International News Photo Inc.
title: Celebrations - Parades - Municipal Events - Armistice Day.
